Definition: a religion founded in Iran in 1863
Example: emphasizes the spiritual unity of all humankind; incorporates Christian and Islamic tenets; many adherents live in the United States; Bahaism has no public rituals or sacraments and praying is done in private
Synonyms: religion, a, founded, in, Iran, emphasizes, the, spiritual, unity, of, all, humankind, incorporates, Christian, and, Islamic, tenets, many, adherents, live, United, States, has, no, public, rituals, or, sacraments, praying, is, done, private
Category: noun.cognition
